This is a plain text kard. Note that <f6> merely changes the colour.
<BR><!title><B>Printing</B><BR>

<html><head><meta name="qrichtext" content="1" /><style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
</style></head><body style=" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Dejavu Sans Mono'; font-size:14pt;"> Printing will generally be slightly better if all text is html, (&gt;Edit &gt;Make Html for each page)  otherwise printing will just be a word dump of the text with words cut off in the middle , etc. At present printing is not all that great but more or less works at least for me.<br /> </span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Dejavu Sans Mono'; font-size:14pt;">  </span></p></body></html>
<BR><!title><B>Customize</B><BR>

<html><head><meta name="qrichtext" content="1" /><style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
</style></head><body style=" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Bitstream Vera Sans';"> If you don't like how things work since the programme and the source are the same thing you can instantly try out your imrovements . For example if you do not like F12 as the short cut for find change the line that reads ' self.findAction.setAccel(Qt.Key_F12 )' to your choice for find. Note that python is </span><span style=" font-family:'Bitstream Vera Sans'; font-weight:600;"> very </span><span style=" font-family:'Bitstream Vera Sans';"> sensitive to the alignment of text so a python capable editor is best. I use xjed.</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><br /></p></body></html>